Authentication : means [ Identify request from which user ]
                ex:  request from inst server (find user)


Authorization : means [ What action user can perform ]
                ex: access of room (student , teacher, director)

                user -> register -> server store data
                server -> genrate Token with signature(JWT_SECRET) -> user
                [every time user request server Identify who?]


Validation :  means [ Check format of data ]
                ex: Email, Phone no. (on signup)


Verfication : means [ data is correct or incorrect ]
                ex: Does it belongs to you like email